## 3. Research Documentation

Academic texts, design rationales, and research documentation included in this
repository are part of doctoral research conducted at Auckland University of Technology (AUT)
and are published under the **MediaFranca** initiative.

These materials are shared for transparency and reproducibility under
**CC BY 4.0** unless otherwise noted.

